{
  "text": "(3) Figure 2 shows the flatness factor F obtained from FDM-RCF using N=128, [CITATION_1] ). Unfortunately, the calculated range of Re \u03bb is not large enough to settle the debate on the power-law transition of the flatness factor at around Re \u03bb =700. Larger size computations are currently under going. ",
  "correct_citation": {
